>Description:
When searching in DrScheme's definitions window, it hilights the correct
text.  However, upon clicking search again, the same number of characters
_following_ the correct text are hilighted instead.
>How-To-Repeat:
Type 
(hi there)
in the definitions pane.
Search for hi.
Click search again.
